questionsAndAnswers.question: What to provide to initiate the process?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Please share the essentials for your project - a vector logo and brand style guide, Your wireframes/sketch, a brief outline of your goals, and some examples/inspirational websites.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What files will constitute the final deliverables?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: The initial deliverables will consist of flat PNG or JPEG files showcasing the website design I've crafted for you. Following that, I will supply the fully editable and development-ready  Figma URL and Figma File. You can modify or pass it on to a developer to convert the website design into code.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How can I place an order for additional pages?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No worries. After discussing your project requirements, I can create a custom offer to meet your needs. Feel free to send me a message.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How should I proceed without wireframes or a brand guideline?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: We can collaborate to gather the necessary information and discuss your vision to create a design that aligns with your preferences and goals. Reach out to start the conversation.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Are you open to redesigning existing websites?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I specialize in redesigning websites for a fresh look and improved performance. Please send me a message to discuss how to revitalize your site.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Does your gig include coding or web development services?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Coding services are available only in the Premium Package. For coding assistance, please send me a direct message FIRST.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you implement the design into WordPress following the Figma stage?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Sure! I have a skilled team of developers ready to transform Figma designs into WordPress websites. Please Note that this would be treated as a separate project with its own pricing and timeline. Drop me a message if you have any more questions or concerns.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Is the pricing for your gig fixed or negotiable?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: The gig price is an estimate and may vary depending on your project requirements. To receive a precise quote and timeline, please get in touch with me before placing an order.
